      <div class="hard">
        Hurricane of Reflection<small class="by">~by Elio Torres</small>
      </div>
      <div class="hard"></div>

      <div>
        <h1 class="text">Hurricane of Reflection</h1>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">The path is not made; the walker makes it as<br>he walks.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Don’t miss the forest because there’s a tree<br>in front of you,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Discover, feel, flirt with the world and<br>love will find you</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Sitting in an old park, sipping a delicious<br>coffee, maybe</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Dancing to a lively rhythm. Don’t stop dreaming,<br>enjoy every moment,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Let life flow, flow yourself too, breathe,<br>live, take on each<br>moment as if it were your last.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Convince yourself that<br>life is only one, don’t<br>hurt anyone along the way,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Turn your sadness into<br>a song and improve it<br>with your actions.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Be a breeze with words, be a hurricane<br>of reflection,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Become a tornado with your actions and<br>revolutionize the world.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Don’t stop searching but let yourself be found, that’s the<br>answer these verses<br>give you,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">and a rude poet keeps repeating it.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Live, Live, Live, accept your mortality, but<br>remember that<br>you are part of the universe,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">made of the<br>elements that<br>nourish the Earth, and that you will return to it.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Tell your loved ones<br>that you love them, give flowers to any woman,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">our destiny is<br>made by us every day, and love flutters like a bird that<br>doesn’t want to be owned.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Climb the mountain of your life,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">descend the<br>skirts of a lady, climb every star you<br>find,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">steal<br>a story from a book, fill children with<br>wonder,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">and remember the<br>one you carry inside.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Don’t charge the<br>bearer for energy,<br>don’t become a traitor, switching<br>sides,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">burn what<br>you wear on the outside, stay alone with your<br>inner self,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">be a<br>superior being, doing what you love every day,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">and never<br>be imprisoned by<br>a love that doesn’t come,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">look ahead and<br>wait—what’s meant for you will arrive.</p>
      </div>

